title: Training Cup - Dr. Brown's Spoutless Insulated Cup
description:
Dr Browns Spoutless Insulated Cup
The easy way for little ones to transition from sippy cups to open cups.  Durable, lightweight and designed to keep drinks fresh and cool, this 10-ounce insulated cup is perfect for helping a little guy or gal transition to a grownup-style cup. Features a spoutless rim that is spill-proof with the one-piece silicone valve in place. Eye-catching, kid-friendly graphics make using this cup fun and exciting.

• Easy to assemble and clean
• Dishwasher safe
• 10 oz/300 ml
• Recommended for babies 12 months +
• Available in a variety of appealing characters and colors
